    "description": "Join the StudyIQ Education Digital Technologies family as a Instructional Designer in Varanasi. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout StudyIQ Education Digital Technologies:\nStudyIQ Education Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Maintain classroom discipline and create a positive learning environment\n• Maintain student records and prepare progress reports\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Special Education\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Research Skills\n• Proficiency in Educational Technology\n• Proficiency in Child Psychology\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n• Proficiency in CBSE/ICSE Standards\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with StudyIQ Education Digital Technologies!",
